{"title":"Summarizing the 'other' conjugations","body":[{"type":"p","text":"Formula: zijn + aan het + infinitive"},{"type":"p","text":"Formula: liggen/zitten/staan/lopen + te + infinitive"},{"type":"p","text":"Formula:"},{"type":"p","text":"Informal: 1st person singular (stem):"},{"type":"p","text":"Formal: 2nd person singular + u:"},{"type":"p","text":"\"Let's\": laten we + infinitive:"},{"type":"p","text":"Formula: zijn/worden/raken + past participle"},{"type":"p","text":"Formula: infinitive"},{"type":"p","text":"Formula: te + infinitive"},{"type":"p","text":"Formula: infinitive + -d"}]}